InstaClone — HOW / PLAN Document 🏗️
________________________________________
1. Vision
Build a production-grade social media platform inspired by Instagram and TikTok focused on:
•	backend engineering
•	distributed systems
•	scalability
•	reliability
•	real-world architecture
•	performance engineering
The goal is not just making a clone.
The goal is becoming strong enough for companies like:
•	Rubrik
•	Stripe
•	Google
•	Uber
________________________________________
2. Engineering Philosophy
Start Simple
Begin with a clean modular monolith.
Do not start with:
•	Kubernetes
•	microservices
•	distributed databases
Add complexity only when needed.
________________________________________
Learn Internals
Understand:
•	why Redis helps
•	why Kafka exists
•	why sharding is needed
•	why caching fails
Avoid tutorial-style engineering.
________________________________________
Build Like Production
Every feature should consider:
•	scale
•	failures
•	retries
•	monitoring
•	security
•	performance
________________________________________
